{
    "scenes": [
        {
            "scene": "1",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "Oh, they&#39;re finally awake.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Huh… Where am I…?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "Boxi, what do you remember from before all of this?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Well...",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "2",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I remember driving.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I was on my way to work… and I remember a… car coming towards me…",
                    "end": false
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "3",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "Is that it?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "After that, I remember everything going black…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "Checks out with their transcript here, it says they were in a nearly fatal car crash.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "Boxi, what year do you remember it being?",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "4",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "That was 2 years ago.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Have I been in a coma for 2 years!?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "It seems so.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I can&#39;t believe this… what about my job?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "That is the reason why we are here, actually.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "The current leader realized that your job was quite important and has replaced you.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "However, he has left you the option of taking a new position.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "You may take it, or find a new job elsewhere.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "He has stated that your gap in history will be erased and not affect your transcript.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Who…?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "Oh, yes. I forgot that his leadership is new to you.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "He was inaugurated not too long ago.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "His name is Stewie (Family Guy).",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Stewie…? I don&#39;t ever remember a Stewie.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "No, his name is Stewie (Family Guy).",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Boxi: Is the subtitle really that important?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "Yes. He demands all those in government positions refer to him as Stewie (Family Guy).",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I see…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "For your position, we will give you a moment to decide whether you take it or not.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "We hope that our stay here was not too unwelcome.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "0",
                    "text": "…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Huh, this is a big decision it seems I have to make here.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Either I start working under a guy I&#39;ve never heard of before, or I have to go job hunting again.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Boxi: What will I choose…?",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "4a",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "Good choice, Boxi&#8211",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "0",
                    "text": "*phone ringing*",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "Let me get it.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "Hello?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "Oh. Yes. Of course. I see.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "Yes, of course, sir. Goodbye.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "0",
                    "text": "*phone hang up*",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "…It was Stewie (Family Guy).",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": "He told me that he got tired of waiting for you to wake up and found a new employee to replace you.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "10",
                    "text": " We apologize for the inconvenience, Boxi.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Oh. I see.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Well, I guess I&#39;ll just go off, then…",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "4b",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Well, I don&#39;t know the guy, or his motives.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "For all I know, I could be working for someone looking to destroy Planet X…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I guess I&#39;ll just see myself out of the hospital, then.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "We understand.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "9",
                    "text": "Thank you for your time, Boxi.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "5",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "At least this place hasn&#39;t changed a lot.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Even if it feels like I was only here yesterday…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I should examine it a bit before going inside, though. Just to make sure.",
                    "end": false
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "5a",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Yup, pretty much looks like the drunken Clam I know.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Nothing super different about it.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "5b",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Huh. There&#39;s a piece of paper hung up on the front of the door here.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "11",
                    "text": "ABSOLUTELY NO FIGHTING UNDER ANY CIRCUMSTANCES WITHIN THE CONFINEMENTS OF THIS ESTABLISHMENT",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "",
                    "text": "",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "5c",
            "item": true,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "12",
                    "text": "Yo. Haven&#39;t seen you around these parts.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Uh, that&#39;s because I…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "You know what, nevermind.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "12",
                    "text": "Well, you seem pretty chill.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "12",
                    "text": "Here, I&#39;ll give you this.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "0",
                    "text": "BOXI OBTAINED THE CHUG JUG!",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Uh, thank you…?",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "5d",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Alright, let&#39;s go in.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "6",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Well, it looks like the inside hasn't changed a whole lot, either. Thankfully.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "6a",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "That’s where I used to usually sit when I would come here a lot. But it seems someone is already sitting there…",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "6b",
            "item": true,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "13",
                    "text": "Hey, haven’t seen you around here.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "13",
                    "text": "The name’s Minecraft Steve, but people just call me Steve.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Uh, that’s cool.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "13",
                    "text": "Hey, you look pretty down. Take this.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "0",
                    "text": "BOXI OBTAINS MINECRAFT STEAK",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "6c",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Hey, that’s a new face.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "What’s got you here so early? You’re not day-drinkin’, are you?",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "7a",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Well, I just got out of a 2 year coma. I think I kind of need a pick-me-up.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Oh man, that’s gotta suck. I couldn’t imagine being in a situation like that…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "But I guess you have to, no?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "If you put it that way, yeah.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "7b",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "What’s it to you? It’s none of your business when I decide to come here.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Woah-hoh, easy there, speedster! Sorry I wanted to just poke a little friendly jab at you.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "8",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Anyways, I’ve been waiting for you. Those agents you saw in the hospital told me you’d probably come here, so they told me to wait at this exact spot. Seems they were right!",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "How did they…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Yeah, it’s a little creepy how much they studied you and your behavior! Makes me wonder what kinda tabs they got on me.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "But still, that’s besides the point. They assigned me to try to help you find another job.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Well, that’s nice, I suppose, but…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "What’s the deal with this, anyways? Wouldn’t they have just laid me off normally?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I don’t think you really understand this, Boxi.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Stewie (Family Guy) knew what you brought to the last leader, and he didn’t want to just let you go.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "He still gave you the option to leave. But in a way, he still wanted to have your skills to use to his advantage.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "When he first came up in the political scene, I was actually his right-hand man.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I helped him grow to be in the position of power that he is now.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "His main goal…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "To make everything a Family Guy Funny Moment.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I wrote every speech he delivered, I was at every press conference, every interview, every meeting…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "But as soon as he got elected, he just… threw me to the wayside. Like trash.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Although they employed me to help you get some other job under him, I think I need my dignity back.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I can’t just help a guy that ditched me so easily! ",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "He’ll do it to you, too, as soon as he doesn’t need your expertise anymore.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "You’re a nice… er… person, Boxi. I can’t let him do that to you.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Even if we’ve only been talking for however long the reader has spent on this specific scene.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "What?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "What? I didn’t say anything.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "8a",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "…Well, this is all very nice of you, uh…",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "8b",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "…Well, I don’t really appreciate your forwardness, uh…",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "9",
            "item": true,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Wait, I just realized I don't know your name.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Uh, it's been on my name tag this entire time. See?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "0",
                    "text": "*a name tag item shows up on screen, its one of those “hello my name is” stickers with “Brian” written on it in the most performative cursive you can think of*",
                    "end": false
                }, 
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Oh. I guess that explains why I feel like I subconsciously knew it this whole time.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "But, I just don't get what was so special about my abilities that Stewie wanted-",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "It's Stewie (Family Guy)",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": " …Okay. I don’t get what… Stewie (Family Guy) wanted out of me so badly, that he was willing to give me a new job entirely.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I mean, I don’t think I was bad at my job, but I also don’t think I was so excellent at it, either.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Well, there is one thing that you could do that no other employee there could.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "What is it?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "You were one of the lucky few able to perform battles.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Which is the exact reason why he wanted to keep you on his side so bad...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "He knew that if you were to go against him, you could easily go up against him and defeat him.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I was by his side for years; he trained harder than anyone I know for the ability to battle.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Some are just naturally born with it.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "And, of course, you, Boxi, are one of those who were gifted with that ability.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "And to this day, you were the best battler in the entirety of Planet X",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Wait... I think I remember...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Yes, I remember now.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "That was the reason they hired me in the first place.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "My battling prowess was so good, they wanted to have me in their sphere to protect from hypothetical invaders.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Although, I mostly got delegated to picking off stragglers.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Like homeless guys and teenagers trying to trespass.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Don't you want to go back to then? The thrill of the battle?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I do miss it...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "But, even though I've been unconscious, and still feel like 2 years ago was yesterday...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I think I'm out of the loop when it comes to battles.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I couldn’t even tell you the last time I did one before all this happened.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "I was mostly doing maintenance work on the building every day.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "Battles happen so infrequently, I think I lost my charm for them…",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Well, that’s exactly what I'm here for, bud.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I need you to rekindle that battling fire deep inside you so that we can stop Stewie (Family Guy) from doing whatever it is he’s planning to do with his power.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "The planet as we know it resides on this one hope...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Or else, who knows what could happen.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "2",
                    "text": "...Like what, exactly?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Well...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "The day before his inauguration, I said one thing to him.",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "scene": "10",
            "item": false,
            "dialogue": [
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Stewie (Family Guy), I want you to know one thing before you get up there.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "After everything we've accomplished here, I don't want you getting too ahead of yourself y'know?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "You're still my best friend, after all.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "1",
                    "text": "Yes, yes, of course.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "1",
                    "text": "Whatever you say, I'll take it into great consideration, Brian.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I know we want everything to be a Family Guy funny moment, but...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "1",
                    "text": "But what?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "If everything is a Family Guy Funny Moment, then nothing is.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "1",
                    "text": "...",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "1",
                    "text": "Oh, quit your nonsense, Brian!",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "1",
                    "text": "You're just trying to get my nerves all up before my big moment.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "No, no, come on!",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "I'm being serious, man.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "You gotta watch yourself.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Just, remember that while you're up there for me, okay?",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "1",
                    "text": "We'll see. I'll see you later, Brian.",
                    "end": false
                },
                {
                    "speaker": "3",
                    "text": "Good luck, Stewie (Family Guy)!",
                    "end": true
                }
            ]
        },
